| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1973 — Recovery Inhibition (nitrogen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0c26951f-ce03-520e-8f00-dbbaf626c8b1"
